headline: PTC to Report Q1 Earnings: Here's What Investors Should Expect
summary: PTC heads into Q1 earnings with revenues guided at $600-$660M, EPS of $1.26-$1.82, and ARR growth seen at 8-8.5% amid a challenging macro.
